---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Track & Tote: a personal space for short essays, blogs, and policy writing with optional data context."
>
  <section class="page-intro">
    <p class="kicker">About</p>
    <h1>Why this exists</h1>
    <p>
      Track &amp; Tote is a personal writing space for short essays, field notes, and public-policy reflections.
      Some pieces are text-first. Some include charts. The intention is always the same: readable writing
      with honest method.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section text-section">
    <h2>What readers should expect</h2>
    <p>Clear language, visible assumptions, and sources that can be checked.</p>
    <p>No inflated certainty. No decorative data for its own sake.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
